text: Rose Eleanor Arbuthnot-Leslie (born 9 February 1987) is a Scottish actress. She is known for her roles as Gwen Dawson in the ITV drama series Downton Abbey and as Ygritte in the HBO fantasy series Game of Thrones. ==References== Category:1987 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from Aberdeen Category:Scottish stage actors Category:Scottish television actors Category:Scottish movie actors Category:Scottish voice actors
